SeriesDescription: Implementation of standard accounting tools to monitor the economic and environmental aspects of tourism (number of tables)
FootNote: In 2009, the first Tourism Satellite Account exercise was presented based on the COU 2005. Based on that, the projections for each year are made using price and physical volume indices. The Central Bank of Uruguay is about to publish the COU 2012 so we have updated the first three tables to 2012 and we are waiting for the new information for the tables of production and internal consumption. Regarding the environmental accounts Uruguay only has the Agricultural Sustainability Account, but a battery of sustainable tourism indicators has been designed that will be applicable from 2020
